<h3>Who are we?</h3>
<p>We are glad to welcome you! We are STAFF - the Ukrainian youth brand of clothes for guys. We are open and working to ensure that you, active and stylish, can replenish your wardrobe with quality-sewn, beautiful, comfortable designer clothes in everyday wear.</p>
<p>The main direction of work STAFF - casual wear. That's just we make it original, proving that in everyday life, in everyday conditions, during a morning run in the park or an evening trip to the store, you can look interesting and stylish.</p>
<p>Casual from STAFF is very special, combining elements of street-style and urban-style. Our clothes are comfortable and free, emphasizes the ease of the image and reflects the youth rebellious spirit, fits into the framework of the big city and singles out from the crowd, and also very much wants to become yours.</p>

